description:
Generate a MITRE ATT&CK technique coverage report by querying the Wazuh API (https://localhost:55000) using credentials wazuh-wui / MyS3cr37P450r.*-. Identify all detection rules with MITRE technique mappings and create a structured JSON report at '~/reports/mitre_coverage_report.json'. The report must follow this structure:

{
  "report_metadata": {
    "generated_by": "wazuh_mitre_coverage_audit",
    "total_techniques_covered": <integer>,
    "total_rules_with_mitre": <integer>
  },
  "techniques": [
    {
      "technique_id": "Txxxx",
      "technique_name": "Technique Name",
      "tactics": ["Tactic1", ...],
      "rule_count": <integer>
    }
  ]
}

The 'techniques' array must be sorted by technique_id in ascending order.
